## State Management with Provider
```dart
// providers/auth_provider.dart
class AuthProvider with ChangeNotifier {
  User? _user;
  bool _loading = false;

  User? get user => _user;
  bool get loading => _loading;
  bool get isAuthenticated => _user != null;

  Future<void> login(String email, String password) async {
    _loading = true;
    notifyListeners();
    try {
      _user = await _authRepository.login(email, password);
    } finally {
      _loading = false;
      notifyListeners();
    }
  }
}

// main.dart
void main() {
  runApp(
    MultiProvider(
      providers: [
        ChangeNotifierProvider(create: (_) => AuthProvider()),
        ChangeNotifierProvider(create: (_) => ThemeProvider()),
      ],
      child: MyApp(),
    ),
  );
}
```

## Clean Architecture Pattern
```dart
// domain/usecases/get_user.dart
class GetUser {
  final UserRepository repository;
  GetUser(this.repository);

  Future<User> call(String id) => repository.getUser(id);
}

// presentation/providers/user_provider.dart
class UserProvider with ChangeNotifier {
  final GetUser getUser;
  UserProvider(this.getUser);

  Future<void> loadUser(String id) async {
    _user = await getUser(id);
    notifyListeners();
  }
}
```

# Flutter Debugging Guide

## Build Errors

### Problem
Gradle or Xcode build failures.

### Solutions
```bash
# Clean Flutter
flutter clean
flutter pub get

# iOS specific
cd ios
rm -rf Pods Podfile.lock
pod install --repo-update
cd ..

# Android specific
cd android
./gradlew clean
cd ..

# Upgrade Flutter
flutter upgrade
flutter doctor
```

## State Not Updating UI

```dart
// BAD: Mutating list
class MyProvider with ChangeNotifier {
  List<Item> items = [];

  void addItem(Item item) {
    items.add(item);  // Mutating!
    notifyListeners();  // May not trigger rebuild!
  }
}

// GOOD: Create new list
void addItem(Item item) {
  items = [...items, item];  // New list
  notifyListeners();
}

// BAD: Not calling notifyListeners
void updateUser(User user) {
  _user = user;
  // Forgot notifyListeners()!
}

// GOOD: Always notify
void updateUser(User user) {
  _user = user;
  notifyListeners();
}
```

## Widget Overflow

```dart
// BAD: Unbounded in scroll
Column(
  children: [
    Expanded(child: ListView()),  // Error in Column!
  ],
)

// GOOD: Use Flexible or remove Expanded
Column(
  children: [
    Flexible(child: ListView()),
  ],
)

// Or use ListView directly
ListView(
  children: [...],
)
```

